  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うわぁ……
ここが&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ村&lt;White&gt;？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa! THIS is Valhalla Village? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あレ……なんかぼくの
知ってる&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ村&lt;White&gt;より
キレイな気がする……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the...the atmosphere here is a lot livelier
than the Valhalla Village I remember...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really? How come? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もともとここは貧しい人が
集まってできた街だったかラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Initially only poor people gathered in this village, but 
then more people started coming in. I suppose it was
only natural to get livelier. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれって、
何年前だったんだっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wonder...how many years it has been since then?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>とにかく、困ってる人探して、
助けるんだよね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyways, we need to find some people to help... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...But before that... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ウロウロしないの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop fooling around! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト、さっき言ってた
ノルンって……
オレらの母ちゃん？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey Eto! That Norn you were talking about a 
while ago...is she supposed to be our mom?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、うん、
……みたいなもの、かな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah? Uh... She kind of is, I guess? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>母ちゃんか～。
どんなかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My own mother... I wonder... 
what kind of person she is...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトがわたしたちの
お母さんでしょ？　ね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto is our mother already, though. Don't you agree? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？
あ、そうかも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really? Uh, 
maybe so...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん……そうだね♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, yes! I guess you're right!!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Maybe add the music note to the end</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトが母ちゃんって
なんかピンと来ねー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto is our loud, nosy, lousy mother...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review translation.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>生意気に育っちゃって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And you, mister, are a very impolite child. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、もう勝手に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah! Oh, he's such a self-centered brat... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_020_010_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>困ってる人探すんでしょ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is HE really supposed to be the
one to help people in need!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
